<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lightning" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lightning,</orth> the flash of light that precedes thunder: <bibl n="shak. ven 348" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 348</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. pp 67" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.201" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 201</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.1.16" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 2, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 1.24" default="NO" valid="yes">John I, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.79" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.129" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 129</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.64" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.177" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.3.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 3, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 1, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.35" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.195" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 195</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.394" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 394</bibl>. <cit><quote>l. flash,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 3</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.270" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 270</bibl>. <cit><quote>a l. before death,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 90</bibl></cit> (a last blazing up of the flame of life).
